snippet.title: Gekitotsu Toma L'Arc: TomaRunner vs L'Arc-en-Ciel - Tomarun Taikai 2000 with Hyde.
snippet.description:
TomaRunner vs L'Arc-en-Ciel - Tomarun Taikai 2000
This time featuring Hyde -- A wry-smiled take handler.

See also other member run:
Tetsu: https://youtu.be/6mcjK5fz0k0
Yuki: https://youtu.be/iKBHoGL4u3Y
Ken: https://youtu.be/9PWbnkdx1iY

About the game:
Gekitotsu Toma LArc: TomaRunner vs LArc-en-Ciel is a Japan-exclusive racing game for the PlayStation. 

It is the sequel to TomaRunner and includes members of the Japanese band LArc-en-Ciel as playable characters. 

Each member of the group voices in the game are the characters themselves. 
The game was popular enough to get PS one books reprint December 21, 2001.
